{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"getter","kind":"keyword"},{"text":"=","kind":"text"},{"text":"isDraggable","kind":"identifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"draggable","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If this property is set to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":", the user can drag the annotation after","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"pressing and holding the view, and the associated annotation object must also","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"implement the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setCoordinate:"},{"text":" method. The default value of this property is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Setting this property to "},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" lets the map view know that the annotation is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"always draggable. In other words, you cannot conditionalize drag operations by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"attempting to stop an operation that has already been initiated; doing so can"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"lead to undefined behavior. Once begun, the drag operation should always"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"continue to completion."}]},{"anchor":"Related-examples","text":"Related examples","type":"heading","level":4},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Enable users to drag "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" objects on your map."}]}]}],"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"draggable","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(py)draggable","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"draggable"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L261","fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h"},"roleHeading":"Instance Property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"draggable","symbolKind":"property"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/draggable","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/draggable"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the annotation view is draggable.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","title":"MLNAnnotationView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/draggable":{"title":"draggable","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"draggable"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the annotation view is draggable."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/draggable","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/draggable"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection","title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"}}}